{"tid":1456563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實識得撒退比留守更難","createTime":"2019-08-12T10:24:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:11:30.000Z","uid":36114,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9dea76461f1500b0aa1fccc1a80ede519038421c","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:24:39.000Z","msg":"留守係需要好大嘅勇氣<br />\n但你識得放低當前嘅熱血去撒<br />\n免得之後比人拉 要其他手足花更多嘅資源去救你地<br />\n呢樣係更加難 要更大嘅勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好同我講人多就一定無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲狗無性唔係第一日知 琴日已經站內tg<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求其講句非法集結去清場已經可以郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係散播失敗 只係想大家衡量下 <br />\n係咪真係要無目的咁留守<br />\n<br />\n非引戰<br />\n<br />\n只係想講 被拉嘅手足 多一個真係好多<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"267b25e6e9ca0ecc13ba4a5088dff5ee72dcbe82","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"自己衡量下啦"},{"pid":"9c137b8b7300e4ba82bd119a27da2e5612c0fc77","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:25:49.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b1e64a65bfebf51ec1d6d422bc3f1d9afae053","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"自製10連推"},{"pid":"5ad2946df5a6cac6361b11867df5b505916b1fb6","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:26:23.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"dd4a5f26d70aa45ca9ca893e0b8b46ea76a34847","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T10:26:47.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"498b3ed84aa23103cf1b014284dbc8a1a9472cc5","tid":1456563,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re